name: Longuinhos Bar, Restaurant & Confectioners

reviews.review_text: Finally got the chance to visit this establishment and I did just that. It's ambience is rustic and ages like fine wine. Coming to the food, we had the Sausage Rolls, Beef Croquettes, and Prawn Pattys and the King Fish Rava Fry, all of them tasted good, but the standout dish was the Sausage Rolls. Pricing is very much value for money and the service can be improved on. Definitely check this place out, as it's one of the few places in Goa that serves quality food.

We tried prawns curry rice here which was very good. But the king fish fry that we ordered was rolled up. And they actually served this to us. The service is pathetic. If your waiter is busy the other waiter will not even take your order. By the time our fish fry arrived (which was rolled up) we finished our beer. They are biased towards their regular customers over tourists.

We stumbled upon this beautiful restaurant in Margoa., very close to MMC market. Wow the food is so cheap and so tasty here that you must visit this place to eat and finger lick. The fish curry rice, the prawn fry, the fish fry, the drinks are dead cheap here and so is the food. Yummy!!! The place is crowded and there is waiting period. All the staff are very courteous and do advise you as well on the type of food and drink. The service is super quick. a must visit for sure

description:
### Longuinhos Bar, Restaurant & Confectioners: A Nostalgic Culinary Gem

Nestled in the bustling area of Aquem, Longuinhos Bar, Restaurant & Confectioners boasts a commendable rating of 3.9 from over 1,700 reviews, marking it as a popular choice among both locals and tourists alike. This charming establishment is celebrated for its comforting dishes, particularly its **pork** offerings (frequently mentioned 26 times), alongside favorites like **beef croquettes** and **beef steak**, both highlighted in the glowing feedback of satisfied diners. Words like “nostalgic” frequently arise in reviews, hinting at the restaurant's ability to evoke fond memories of traditional Goan cuisine.

### Ambiance & Design

Upon entering Longuinhos, guests are greeted with a rustic charm that seems to age like fine wine. The décor features warm, earthy tones complemented by wooden furnishings that create a cozy yet lively atmosphere. Customer-submitted images depict a vibrant setting featuring smiling patrons enjoying their meals against the backdrop of quaint table arrangements and modest yet tastefully chosen decorations. The lighting is soft and inviting, enhancing the overall dining experience, while the buzz of conversation fills the air, punctuated by laughter and the clinking of glasses—a perfect ambiance for both an intimate meal or a casual gathering.

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The culinary experience at Longuinhos is as diverse as it is delectable. Reviewers rave about several standout dishes. The **Sausage Rolls** garnered special mention as the standout favorite, and are artistically presented, showcasing crispy dough wrapped around a savory filling. Patrons also enjoyed the mouth-watering **Beef Croquettes** and **Prawn Patties**; the latter's golden crust and succulent interior can delight anyone who takes a bite. Seafood lovers will find solace in the **King Fish Rava Fry**, though some noted inconsistencies in its preparation. The prices are remarkably affordable, adding to the restaurant's appeal as a value-for-money destination. 

The menu also caters to various dietary preferences, offering both meat-centric and vegetarian options, making it an inclusive choice for groups.

### Customer Experience & Service

While Longuinhos earns praise for its food, customer service has been a focal point of mixed reviews. Many diners appreciated the friendliness of the staff, who were noted to be knowledgeable and willing to advise on menu choices, as referred by several customers. However, a few reviews highlight challenges with service efficiency, particularly during peak dining hours, where diners felt neglected if their assigned waitstaff was busy. A mention of bias toward regular customers over occasional visitors suggests a need for fine-tuning in service practices to enhance overall guest experience. Despite these shortcomings, several reviews commend the quick service during less crowded times.

### Popularity & Reviews

Longuinhos seems to have solidified its status as a beloved spot in the area, with many guests recommending it as a must-visit. The restaurant's popularity is underscored by the crowded environments observed by patrons, inferring a robust local following. Social media buzz echoes these sentiments, often showcasing the restaurant's vibrant dishes and welcoming environment. Though the restaurant has not received notable critic accolades, the sheer volume of positive reviews and the enthusiastic recommendations serve as a testament to its charm and culinary prowess.

### Utilizing Visual Content

The customer-provided images are a delightful addition to the narrative, showcasing not only food but also the warm and inviting space that Longuinhos offers. One striking photo captures the enticing **Prawn Patties** on a vibrant yellow plate, while another reveals diners enjoying their meals, embodying the blissful and lively vibe of the restaurant. Each image serves to transport potential customers into the heart of Longuinhos, enhancing the allure it has built within its community.

In conclusion, Longuinhos Bar, Restaurant & Confectioners is more than just a dining establishment; it's a tapestry woven from flavors, memories, and community spirit. Whether you’re in the mood for a nostalgic trip down culinary lane or simply looking for good food at reasonable prices, this restaurant is indeed deserving of a visit.
